---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Individual Health & Dental Plans | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Prescription drug, dental, vision, and paramedical coverage for Ontarians without group benefits. Independent health insurance advice from Heidi Blondin Financial."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Individual Health & Dental Plans</h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-white/65 mt-5 leading-relaxed">
        OHIP covers a lot — but not everything. If you're self-employed, retired, or between jobs, an individual health and dental plan fills the gaps that government coverage leaves behind.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Who needs individual health coverage</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Group benefits through an employer are one of the most common ways Ontarians access extended health coverage. But when you leave a job, start a business, retire early, or simply don't have access to a group plan, your healthcare costs don't disappear — they just stop being reimbursed.</p>
        <p>Individual health and dental plans provide private coverage for expenses that fall outside OHIP: prescription drugs, dental work, vision care, physiotherapy, chiropractic, massage therapy, and more. We help you find coverage that fits your situation and health needs without paying for benefits you won't use.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        {[
          { title: 'Prescription drugs', desc: 'Coverage for eligible prescription medications, often with a drug formulary that covers most common medications.' },
          { title: 'Dental care', desc: 'Preventive (cleanings, x-rays), basic restorative (fillings), and major (crowns, bridges) coverage — plans vary by benefit level.' },
          { title: 'Vision care', desc: 'Eye exams and prescription glasses or contact lenses covered up to a plan maximum every two years.' },
          { title: 'Paramedical services', desc: 'Physiotherapy, massage therapy, chiropractic care, naturopathy, acupuncture, and more — covered up to annual maximums.' },
          { title: 'Hospital coverage', desc: 'Private or semi-private room upgrades when OHIP only covers a ward bed.' },
          { title: 'Emergency travel medical', desc: 'Some plans include emergency out-of-province or out-of-country medical coverage for short trips.' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-brand-tintSage p-5">
            <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-4" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Timing matters</h2>
        <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
          <p>Many individual health plans have a "guaranteed acceptance" window when you leave a group benefit plan — typically 60–90 days. During this window, you can get coverage without medical questions or exclusions for pre-existing conditions. Once that window closes, applying becomes harder if you have health issues.</p>
          <p>If you're changing jobs, retiring, or leaving a group plan for any reason, reach out to us early so we can make sure you don't miss this window.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-brand-tintPlum p-5 border-l-2 border-brand-plum/30">
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-ink/55 leading-relaxed">Insurance products are offered through Heidi Blondin Financial / Qualified Financial Services. Coverage details vary by plan and insurer. This article is for general information purposes only. Please consult with a qualified advisor to determine what coverage is appropriate for your situation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Find the right health coverage" sub="Book a free consultation and we'll match you with a plan that covers what you actually need." />

</BaseLayout>
